    "17625385448d4f1537": {
      "type": "_blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "ai_gen_block_ac97d9c_HKYRqk": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_ac97d9c",
          "settings": {
            "background_image": "shopify://shop_images/Bloom_Culture_LLAYTON-138_copy.webp",
            "section_padding_top": 100,
            "section_padding_bottom": 50,
            "card_width": 60,
            "slide_height": 500,
            "image_width": 50,
            "mobile_image_height": 300,
            "mobile_text_height": 300,
            "card_bg_color": "#f7f6f0",
            "border_color": "#131f15",
            "border_width": 1,
            "text_box_bg_color": "#f7f6f0",
            "text_color": "#131f15",
            "text_box_max_width": 450,
            "show_stars": false,
            "star_size": 18,
            "star_color": "#ffd700",
            "quote_font_size": 14,
            "author_font_size": 14,
            "subtitle_font_size": 12,
            "arrow_bg_color": "#f1f1f1",
            "arrow_color": "#131f15",
            "dot_color": "#f7f6f0",
            "slide_1_image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_5261_101c6581-1e50-44ea-83cb-bca1c7982c31.jpg",
            "slide_1_quote": "<p>“Amazing!! I was nervous to DIY my wedding flowers but it went so smoothly, and they were beautiful! It is overwhelming at first but then it gets easier as you go. Believe it or not we assembled ours the night before and it was a great bonding activity with all the bridesmaids before the big day!”</p>",
            "slide_1_author": "Emily G.",
            "slide_1_subtitle": "",
            "slide_1_rating": 5,
            "slide_2_image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6265.jpg",
            "slide_2_quote": "<p>“I was really intimidated about the thought of doing flowers myself but Alison was so helpful and answered all my questions. She gave me so much hope and confidence during the whole process. Such an incredible experience.”</p>",
            "slide_2_author": "Karly L.",
            "slide_2_subtitle": "",
            "slide_2_rating": 5,
            "slide_3_image": "shopify://shop_images/329109590_1152726628780226_8178488036063305957_n.jpg",
            "slide_3_quote": "<p>“Alison with Bloom Culture really puts SO much work into making the DIY process as easy as possible! Her YouTube videos and DIY proposal guides are extremely detailed, and it was honestly a blast to put together my own florals for my wedding. I got to make everything exactly the way I envisioned, and the flowers turned out sooooo beautiful! Such a great experience!”</p>",
            "slide_3_author": "Claire F.",
            "slide_3_subtitle": "",
            "slide_3_rating": 5,
            "slide_4_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_6483441_8.jpg",
            "slide_4_quote": "<p>“I did a lot of searching and looking into different DIY flower companies. As soon as I came across Bloom Culture and read some of the reviews I knew I wanted to go with them! Alison was so friendly and personable and so easy to work with. With all of the detailed instructions and recipes they provided, putting together the flowers was honestly a breeze once we got started. Overall very happy with the quality of the flowers, the price, and the excellent customer service. Cannot recommend enough!”</p>",
            "slide_4_author": "Ella B.",
            "slide_4_subtitle": "",
            "slide_4_rating": 5,
            "slide_5_image": "shopify://shop_images/6B45C390-7F0C-46CE-A32C-32CAD526872B_2.jpg",
            "slide_5_quote": "<p>“Working with Bloom Culture was so fun and easy. DIY-ing wedding flowers seemed a little scary at first, but Alison’s guides and video tutorials made the process extremely easy. Creating all of the arrangements with my friends and bridesmaids was one of the most memorable and special moments leading up to the wedding.”</p>",
            "slide_5_author": "Alyssa B.",
            "slide_5_subtitle": "",
            "slide_5_rating": 5,
            "slide_6_quote": "",
            "slide_6_author": "",
            "slide_6_subtitle": "",
            "slide_6_rating": 5,
